", \"questionType\": \"TRUE_FALSE\", \"questionOrder\": 14, \"studentAnswers\": [\"错误\"], \"questionContent\": \"Java中，抽象类不能被实例化。\"}, {\"id\": 35, \"points\": 5, \"options\": [{\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"A\", \"optionContent\": \"正确\"}, {\"isCorrect\": true, \"optionKey\": \"B\", \"optionContent\": \"错误\"}, {\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"C\", \"optionContent\": \"\"}, {\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"D\", \"optionContent\": \"\"}], \"isGraded\": true, \"givenScore\": 0.0, \"questionId\": 35, \"questionText\": \"Java中，接口可以包含具体方法的实现。\", \"questionType\": \"TRUE_FALSE\", \"questionOrder\": 15, \"studentAnswers\": [\"正确\"], \"questionContent\": \"Java中，接口可以包含具体方法的实现。\"}, {\"id\": 39, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"implements\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 39, \"questionText\": \"Java中，用于实现接口的关键字是______。\", \"questionType\": \"FILL_BLANK\", \"questionOrder\": 16, \"studentAnswers\": \"asfgfhdgjfhjg\", \"questionContent\": \"Java中，用于实现接口的关键字是______。\"}, {\"id\": 41, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"abstract\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 41, \"questionText\": \"Java中，用于定义抽象类的关键字是______。\", \"questionType\": \"FILL_BLANK\", \"questionOrder\": 17, \"studentAnswers\": \"sdgfhgjhmj,k\", \"questionContent\": \"Java中，用于定义抽象类的关键字是______。\"}, {\"id\": 45, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"[{\\\"type\\\": \\\"TEXT\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"Java集合框架以Collection接口为根，List和Set是其子接口，Map是独立的接口。List接口的实现类有ArrayList、LinkedList等；Set接口的实现类有HashSet、TreeSet等；Map接口的实现类有HashMap、TreeMap等。\\\"}]\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 45, \"questionText\": \"请说明Java中集合框架的层次结构。\", \"questionType\": \"SUBJECTIVE\", \"questionOrder\": 18, \"studentAnswers\": \"sfdgfdhgtjfhkgjlhjgdfsdafsgfhdgjhfg\", \"questionContent\": \"请说明Java中集合框架的层次结构。\"}, {\"id\": 195, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"import java.util.Scanner;\\npublic class Solution {\\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);\\n        int a = scanner.nextInt();\\n        int b = scanner.nextInt();\\n        System.out.println(a + b);\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 195, \"questionText\": \"编写一个Java程序，计算两个整数的和并输出结果。程序需要从标准输入读取两个整数，计算它们的和，然后输出结果。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 使用Scanner类读取输入\\n2. 计算两数之和\\n3. 输出结果\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 19, \"studentAnswers\": [\"import java.util.Scanner;\\n\\npublic class Solution {\\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);\\n        int a = scanner.nextInt();\\n        int b = scanner.nextInt();\\n        System.out.println(a + b);\\n    }\\n}\"], \"questionContent\": \"编写一个Java程序，计算两个整数的和并输出结果。程序需要从标准输入读取两个整数，计算它们的和，然后输出结果。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 使用Scanner类读取输入\\n2. 计算两数之和\\n3. 输出结果\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 200, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr) {\\n        if (arr == null || arr.length <= 1) {\\n            return;\\n        }\\n        int n = arr.length;\\n        for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {\\n            for (int j = 0; j < n - i - 1; j++) {\\n                if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1]) {\\n                    int temp = arr[j];\\n                    arr[j] = arr[j + 1];\\n                    arr[j + 1] = temp;\\n                }\\n            }\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 200, \"questionText\": \"实现冒泡排序算法，对整数数组进行升序排序。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr)\\n2. 原地排序，修改原数组\\n3. 使用冒泡排序算法\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 20, \"studentAnswers\": [\"public class Solution {\\n    public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr) {\\n        if (arr == null || arr.length <= 1) {\\n            return;\\n        }\\n        int n = arr.length;\\n        for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {\\n            for (int j = 0; j < n - i - 1; j++) {\\n                if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1]) {\\n                    int temp = arr[j];\\n                    arr[j] = arr[j + 1];\\n                    arr[j + 1] = temp;\\n                }\\n            }\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\"], \"questionContent\": \"实现冒泡排序算法，对整数数组进行升序排序。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr)\\n2. 原地排序，修改原数组\\n3. 使用冒泡排序算法\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}]}','127.0.0.1','2025-11-04 09:50:18','2025-11-04 10:00:26',NULL,0,NULL,NULL);
